Fires an output when entities enter and exit the trigger volume.

Note: only triggers when the first entity enters the volume and when the last entity leaves the volume.
To listen for individual entities, use `trigger_individual`.

@attribute scope Scope The scope of entities to listen for.
@attribute start_disabled "Start Disabled" Start with this trigger disabled.
@attribute trigger_once "Trigger Once" Disable the trigger after it has been triggered.